snippet.title: Rock Stars Who Haven't Realized They Aren't Famous Anymore
snippet.description:
Some rock stars live fast and die young. Others live fast and get old anyway. It’s one thing to party like you’re 27 when you’re 27, but if you’re still doing it at 60, people are going to start talking. Some famous rockers change with the times, maturing both as human beings and musicians. These… are not those rock stars.

It can be hard to accept that you’re a bit outdated, but these rockers don’t have to worry about that — they still haven’t accepted it. In a lot of cases, the scandals even outweigh the music. Here are some rock stars who haven’t realized they just aren’t that famous anymore.

#CourtneyLove #AxlRose #TommyLee
